snippet.title: Lady Pac (Ms. Pac-Man arcade game clone for Commodore 64) (by Luca Carminati, LC-Games)
snippet.description:
Download Lady Pac from https://lowcarb.itch.io

Lady Pac is a homage to Ms. Pac-Man, an arcade game by Midway in 1982.
Main differences from the original version:
 - Randomly generated mazes
 - Bonus rounds

Author: Luca Carminati (lucacarminati1967@gmail.com)
